<a class="Title2" id="operations-sur-la-fusion-de-donnees_fusion-de-donnees" href="#operations-sur-la-fusion-de-donnees">Fusion de données</a>
</h2><br><pre class="GCode1 Code1 AceCode" data-mode="c_cpp" data-theme="gruvbox" data-bg-color="transparent" style="background-color: transparent;">//===============================================
int first[] = {5,10,15,20,25};
int second[] = {50,40,30,20,10};
std::vector&lt;int&gt; v(10);

std::sort (first, first + 5);
std::sort (second, second + 5);
std::merge (first, first + 5, second, second + 5, v.begin());
//===============================================
A = 5 10 15 20 25;
B = 10 20 30 40 50;
C = 5 10 10 15 20 20 25 30 40 50;
//===============================================</pre><br></div>
